d3f:C4.5 a sh:NodeShape ;
    rdfs:comment "C4.5 is an algorithm that is strongly based off ID3. It creates decision trees the same way as ID3. C4.5 improves on several aspects of ID3, including handling discreet variables, handling training data with missing values, and has the ability to automatically prune the decision trees it creates." ;
    sh:closed true ;
    sh:ignoredProperties ( rdf:type ) ;
    sh:targetClass d3f:C4.5 .

d3f:C5.0 a sh:NodeShape ;
    rdfs:comment "C5.0 is the next version of C4.5, which in turn is the upgrade from ID3. The only difference between C5.0 and C4.5 is some improvements made to C5.0." ;
    sh:closed true ;
    sh:ignoredProperties ( rdf:type ) ;
    sh:targetClass d3f:C5.0 .

