d3f:CWE-1007 a sh:NodeShape ;
    rdfs:label "Insufficient Visual Distinction of Homoglyphs Presented to User" ;
    rdfs:comment "The product displays information or identifiers to a user, but the display mechanism does not make it easy for the user to distinguish between visually similar or identical glyphs (homoglyphs), which may cause the user to misinterpret a glyph and perform an unintended, insecure action." ;
