d3f:CWE-61 a sh:NodeShape ;
    rdfs:label "UNIX Symbolic Link (Symlink) Following" ;
    rdfs:comment "The product, when opening a file or directory, does not sufficiently account for when the file is a symbolic link that resolves to a target outside of the intended control sphere. This could allow an attacker to cause the product to operate on unauthorized files." ;
