d3f:CWE-99 a sh:NodeShape ;
    rdfs:label "Improper Control of Resource Identifiers ('Resource Injection')" ;
    rdfs:comment "The product receives input from an upstream component, but it does not restrict or incorrectly restricts the input before it is used as an identifier for a resource that may be outside the intended sphere of control." ;
