    rdfs:label "Digital Artifact" ;
    rdfs:comment "An information-bearing artifact (object) that is, or is encoded to be used with, a digital computer system. This concept is broad to include the literal instances of an artifact, or an implicit summarization of changes to or properties of other artifacts." ;
