    rdfs:comment "A job schedule contains specification of tasks to be executed at particular times or time intervals.  The schedule is a plan that enacted by a task scheduling process. In Windows, the schedule can be accessed at 'C:\\Windows\\System32\\Tasks' or in the registry. In Linux, the schedule is located at '/etc/crontab'" ;
