    rdfs:comment "An intentionally constrained operating mode of a system in which nonessential functions are disabled or limited and control is shifted to a minimal, well-tested configuration that prioritizes preventing harm (to the system, its environment, or data), maintaining basic stability and monitoring, and enabling diagnosis and recovery back to normal operation." ;
    sh:closed true ;
